image_analysis.description: A photograph of an interior staircase. The stairs are made of polished dark wood with a black wrought-iron railing featuring ornate scrollwork. At the top landing of the stairs, there is a highly decorative, antique-style wooden chair with green upholstery. The ceiling above the staircase is painted with a blue sky and white cloud mural, bordered by gold-leaf ornate molding and a decorative frieze with classical motifs.
image_analysis.layout: The image is a vertical shot looking up a flight of stairs toward a landing.
